the assessment facilitators are comprised of a faculty member and the associate dean from each college, as well as the director of assessment. in addition, the library and division of student affairs both have a representative. the purposes of this group include reviewing and analyzing program assessment reports, sharing best practices on program assessment, and aiding departments and programs in implementing sound assessment practices. tianqin (kelly) shi interim accreditation director meg virick associate dean radha aravamudhan adjunct professor, aerospace engineering lynne andonian professor, occupational therapy valerie mendoza associate professor, art and art history colton saylor , lecturer, english and comparative literature contact the team members directly or email us by area: accreditation@sjsu.edu academicassessment@sjsu.edu online@sjsu.edu programplanning@sjsu.edu  hours: mondays to fridays from 8:00 a.m. to 5:00 p.m. closed for most holidays and for lunch daily, 12:00 p.m. to 1:00 pm. 